msgctxt "92_Erena"
msgid "Hey, Akiyama-san... Wanna go out on a date with me?"
msgstr "Hey, Akiyama-san... Wanna go out on a date with me?"

msgctxt "104_Akiyama"
msgid "A date? Sure, I wouldn't mind that. But you sound kinda tired. Something wrong?"
msgstr "A date? Sure, I wouldn't mind that. But you sound kinda tired. Something wrong?"

msgctxt "116_Erena"
msgid "Nah, I'm fine... Guess I'm still not totally over my ex."
msgstr "Nah, I'm fine... Guess I'm still not totally over my ex."

msgctxt "128_Akiyama"
msgid "Oh, right... How about we paint the town red today to take your mind off him?"
msgstr "Oh, right... How about we paint the town red today to take your mind off him?"

msgctxt "140_Erena"
msgid "Really!? That sounds fun!"
msgstr "Really!? That sounds fun!"

msgctxt "152_Akiyama"
msgid "Good. Where should I meet you?"
msgstr "Good. Where should I meet you?"

msgctxt "164_Erena"
msgid "The usual place?"
msgstr "The usual place?"

msgctxt "176_Akiyama"
msgid "Theater Square? Heheh... What if we see that couple again?"
msgstr "Theater Square? Heheh... What if we see that couple again?"

msgctxt "188_Erena"
msgid "Haha! That'd be pretty funny."
msgstr "Haha! That'd be pretty funny."

msgctxt "200_Erena"
msgid "Well, bye. I'll be waiting for ya!"
msgstr "Well, bye. I'll be waiting for ya!"

msgctxt "212_Akiyama"
msgid "Okay, see you soon."
msgstr "Okay, see you soon."

